---
title: Gyoza-Style Burger with Sugar Snap Slaw and Lime Mayo
description: Dumplings are universally beloved in all cuisines! We've loaded gyoza-inspired flavours into a Canadian favourite – the burger! Sweet sugar snap peas and carrots add fresh crunch to the slaw.
